Transparency includes:
‚Ä¢	Budgets and spending
Every project, contract, and expenditure visible to the public in real time.
‚Ä¢	Decision making processes
Meeting minutes, policy drafts, and rationale for decisions openly accessible.
‚Ä¢	Performance metrics
