‚Ä¢	Leader accountability
Public disclosure of:
‚Ä¢	financial status
‚Ä¢	assets and liabilities
‚Ä¢	conflicts of interest
‚Ä¢	gifts, donations, and external relationships
This prevents corruption, power accumulation, and hidden agendas.
2. High Bandwidth Citizen Input
Transparency is only half the equation.
