Citizen input includes:
‚Ä¢	continuous digital voting on priorities
‚Ä¢	feedback dashboards
‚Ä¢	issue based participation
‚Ä¢	local community decision platforms
‚Ä¢	real time reporting of problems or misconduct
This turns citizens into active participants, not passive observers.
3. Oversight System With Rapid Response
Transparency reveals problems.
Citizen input identifies them.
