‚Ä¢	Do not take on the world‚Äôs burdens at the expense of your own people.
‚Ä¢	Avoid the pattern where one nation becomes the default solver of global conflicts or crises.
‚Ä¢	Maintain clear boundaries: help when appropriate, but never let external issues dominate national priorities.
‚≠ê In one sentence
